Have a look at the following code. Which of the statements is correct?

```java
interface StringOperation {
    String manipulate(String str1);
}
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        StringOperation upperCase = String::toUpperCase;
        StringOperation replaceChar = (input) -> input.replace("<", "=");

        String resultAfterToUpperCase = upperCase.manipulate("iris < ChatGPT");
        String resultAfterReplace = replaceChar.manipulate(resultAfterToUpperCase);
        System.out.println("Ranking of LLMs: " + resultAfterReplace);
    }
}
```

Based on the code below, indicate the corresponding output.

```java
enum ChatApplication {
    MOODLE, ZULIP, SLACK, DISCORD;
    public int getUserNumbers() {
        return switch (this) {
            case MOODLE   -> 100;
            case ZULIP    -> 250;
            case SLACK    -> 500;
            case DISCORD  -> 1000;
        };
    }
}
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        ChatApplication chatApp = ChatApplication.SLACK;
        System.out.println("The chat app " + chatApp + " is used by " + chatApp.getUserNumbers() + " users.");
    }
}
```

Students of a philosophy course are voting on a communication channel. The votes are saved in a `List<Integer>`. What is the output when the `main` method is executed?

```java
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        List<Integer> channelVotes = new ArrayList<>();
        // votes for Email
        channelVotes.add(62);
        // votes for Discord
        channelVotes.add(96);
        // votes for Zulip
        channelVotes.add(58);
        // votes for WhatsApp
        channelVotes.add(43);

        Collections.sort(channelVotes, new Comparator<Integer>() {
            @Override
            public int compare(Integer val1, Integer val2) {
                return val2 - val1;
            }
        });
        System.out.println("The communication channel with the most votes has received "
            + channelVotes.get(0) + " votes.");
    }
}
```
